BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 678.00 Tm (1.  All equipment including chairs, tables, rostrums and PA system that are made available) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 664.00 Tm (in the booked space cannot be moved out of that space.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 645.00 Tm (2.  Food or drinks are not allowed inside the booked space unless permission has been) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 631.00 Tm (obtained from the space administrator.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 612.00 Tm (3.  The space administrator is only responsible for providing the space and basic) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 598.00 Tm (facilities. Any other requirement needs to be specifically requested from the relevant) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 584.00 Tm (provider.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 565.00 Tm (4.  The space administrator is not responsible for the safety of equipment borrowed from) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 551.00 Tm (other departments or providers.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 532.00 Tm (5.  Permission for the usage of an external PA system must first be obtained from the space) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 518.00 Tm (administrator. Consideration will only be given if it is relevant to the event/activity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 499.00 Tm (6.  Users are responsible for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 480.00 Tm (a\)  Managing and arranging any requirement relevant to the event/activity such as) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 466.00 Tm (chairs and tables for registration and refreshment, traffic control and signboards) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 452.00 Tm (from the campus Security Office, backdrop, and other requirements as allowed by UiTM.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 435.00 Tm (b\)  Ensuring that all lights and air-conditioners are switched off before leaving the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 421.00 Tm (space.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 404.00 Tm (c\)  Ensuring that the projector and computers are switched off and in good condition) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 390.00 Tm (before leaving the space.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 1 0 0 1 82.00 373.00 Tm (d\)  Returning the space in a clean and tidy condition after use.) Tj ET
